Split Bills
Split Bills
Split Bills is an application that allows you to manage shared expenses in a simple and transparent way.
The application will prove invaluable when managing expenses while traveling during holidays or business trips. It will help in the daily settlement of expenses of roommates or household members and additionally show the most expensive categories generating the highest costs.
Split Bills is dedicated for:
roommates
- settlement of common costs related to the rented apartment.
families
- settlement of common costs related to the functioning of the family, shopping for grandparents and settlement of contributory gifts.
friends
- accounting for joint trips to the cinema, pizzeria or bar.
