Charts
charts you will learn about the structure of expenses
The Moon:
Thanks to bar charts you will learn about the structure of expenses broken down into individual categories. In addition, all expenses can be grouped to track expenses within specific thematic groups such as:
family shopping
weekend trip
shopping for grandparents
contributing birthday present
utility fees and services
The application allows you to track expenses in any currencies and presents the current balance on a consistent view. The interface has been designed in such a way as to minimize the probability of incorrect input of expenses. In addition, the application allows you to take photos of receipts or purchase documents to have them with you even if you ever lose or destroy them.
The Split Bills application works without internet and you can do everything offline. Transaction data or other data saved in the application are not sent to the probadoSoft external servers and remain secure only on your device.
